          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1711449387038-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>double cream </strong>with your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> [250ml]</span><strong> boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>creamy stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1711449390354-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1711449390354-x400.jpg",
