          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained tagliatelle</strong> to the sauce and stir everything together – this is your <strong>creamy salmon & courgette sauce with fresh tagliatelle</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
